<li><a href="http://webtext.library.yale.edu/xml2html/music.ives-sinclair.nav.html" class="external text" title="http://webtext.library.yale.edu/xml2html/music.ives-sinclair.nav.html" rel="nofollow">A Descriptive Catalogue of the Music of Charles Ives, online edition</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.ivesconcertpark.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.ivesconcertpark.com/" rel="nofollow">The Charles Ives Center for the Arts. Inc</a></li>
<li><a href="http://artofthestates.org/cgi-bin/composer.pl?comp=33" class="external text" title="http://artofthestates.org/cgi-bin/composer.pl?comp=33" rel="nofollow">Art of the States: Charles Ives</a> two works by the composer</li>
<li><a href="http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&amp;GRid=533" class="external text" title="http://www.findagrave.com/cgi-bin/fg.cgi?page=gr&amp;GRid=533" rel="nofollow">Charles Ives</a> at <a href="/wiki/Find_A_Grave" title="Find A Grave">Find A Grave</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.musicweb.uk.net/Ives/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.musicweb.uk.net/Ives/index.htm" rel="nofollow">A Charles Ives Website</a></li>
<li><a href="http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n80-35835" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/identities/lccn-n80-35835" rel="nofollow">Works by or about Charles Ives</a> in libraries (<a href="/wiki/WorldCat" title="WorldCat">WorldCat</a> catalog)</li>
<li><i>Multitasking,</i> an episode of <a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Infinite_Mind&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="The Infinite Mind (page does not exist)">The Infinite Mind</a> public radio program (Cambridge, MA, Lichtenstein Creative Media, 2005), a report on Charles Ives and his integration of multitasking into his compositions.</li>
<li><a href="http://myspace.com/ivesvocalmarathon" class="external text" title="http://myspace.com/ivesvocalmarathon" rel="nofollow">Ives Vocal Marathon</a>—performances and programs of Ives's vocal work.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pytheasmusic.org/ives.html" class="external text" title="http://www.pytheasmusic.org/ives.html" rel="nofollow">Charles Ives at Pytheas Center for Contemporary Music</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.imslp.org/wiki/Category:Ives,_Charles_Edward" class="extiw" title="scores:Category:Ives, Charles Edward">Free scores by Charles Ives</a> in the <a href="/wiki/International_Music_Score_Library_Project" title="International Music Score Library Project">International Music Score Library Project</a></li>
<li>The online music review <a href="http://www.lafolia.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.lafolia.com/" rel="nofollow">La Folia</a> has an in-depth article on <a href="http://www.lafolia.com/archive/covell/covell200411concord.html" class="external text" title="http://www.lafolia.com/archive/covell/covell200411concord.html" rel="nofollow">Ives' Concord Sonata</a></li>
</ul>


